OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable cloud, and some sunny
OL,6,Fspells through the morning. Showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping across northern parts by
OL,8,Fmid-afternoon, before spreading south
OL,9,Flater. These occasionally heavy with a
OL,10,Fvery isolated rumble of thunder
OL,11,Fpossible. Light winds, and feeling
OL,12,Fwarm in any sunny spells.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers fading through the
OL,15,Fevening, with some brief clear spells
OL,16,Flikely. Low cloud, mist and the odd
OL,17,Fspot of drizzle then spreading
OL,18,Fsouthwest after midnight. Less cold
OL,19,Fthan recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
